 His concern grew when Goel texted him in coded messages, and insisted on d=
iscussing trades only in person.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CIt was great to make money,=E2=80=9D =
Niranjan said. =E2=80=9CAt the same time, I was concerned. I told him I hop=
