<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Niranjan said one day he got a text from Goel =
to play squash after work and despite first going out for some drinks he sh=
owed up. It was there that Goel recommended buying options in Lumos Pharma =
Inc., a company Niranjan said he never heard of.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The next day Goel texted him, =E2=80=9CDid you=
