ustomer at 100 cents on the dollar.=E2=80=9D (The bidder is you, in a fake =
mustache, using the money you stole.)</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5p=
x;">Say to customers =E2=80=9Cokay great, so, all we need is for you to fil=
