</ol>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">There are various problems here. (For one thin=
g, Steps 1 and 2 could get you in very bad trouble with the authorities eve=
n before you get to Step 3. For another thing, this plan entails stealing f=
rom people who can=E2=80=99t pass KYC checks, and some=C2=A0people can=E2=
=80=99t pass KYC checks because they are very bad people indeed, and do you=
 really want to steal from them?) Also I do not think that FTX Trading Ltd.=
 followed this plan, because (1) it wasn=E2=80=99t known for being=C2=A0<em=
>particularly </em>lax about KYC and (2) it=E2=80=99s not like anyone is go=
ing around saying that FTX is going to pay anyone back at 100 cents on the =
dollar or anything like that.</p>
